CalculatedFields.Expression: ifelse( module='auto_scale' OR module='ec2_instance'                          , parseDecimal(split({option_details}, ';', 9)), NULL)
CalculatedFields.Name: CPU_Maximum

CalculatedFields.Expression:
// FIXME:  find the way to have a cross account links (URL that includes account)
// FIXME:  adjust Autoscaling pattern
ifelse( 
    module = 'ec2_instance' AND recommendationsourcetype = 'Ec2Instance',     //arn:aws:ec2:eu-west-1:432493493810:instance/i-0ac47f914c0f442b3
     concat('https://console.aws.amazon.com/ec2/v2/home?region=', region, '#InstanceDetails:instanceId=', split(split(arn, ':',6 ), '/',2)),
    (module = 'ec2_instance' AND recommendationsourcetype = 'AutoScalingGroup') OR module = 'auto_scale', 
     concat('https://console.aws.amazon.com/ec2/v2/home?region=', region, '#InstanceDetails:instanceId=', split(split(arn, ':',6 ), '/',2)),
    module = 'ebs_volume', 
    concat('https://console.aws.amazon.com/ec2/v2/home?region=', region, '#VolumeDetails:volumeId=', split(split(arn, ':',6 ), '/',2)),
    module = 'lambda', 
    concat('https://console.aws.amazon.com/lambda/home?region=', region, '#/functions/', name),
    NULL
)
CalculatedFields.Name: Console URL

CalculatedFields.Expression: ifelse( module = 'ec2_instance' or module = 'auto_scale', split({option_to}, '.', 1) , NULL )
CalculatedFields.Name: Family To

CalculatedFields.Expression:
ifelse(
    finding='OPTIMIZED' or finding = 'Optimized', 0,
    finding='UNDER_PROVISIONED', 1,
    finding='OVER_PROVISIONED' OR finding='NOT_OPTIMIZED'  or finding = 'NotOptimized', -1,
    -100
)
CalculatedFields.Name: Findings

CalculatedFields.Expression: ifelse( module = 'ec2_instance' or module = 'auto_scale', split({option_from}, '.', 1) , NULL )
CalculatedFields.Name: From Family Type

CalculatedFields.Expression:
ifelse(
     ${GroupBy} = 'Business Entity', bu,
     ${GroupBy} = 'Business Unit', bu,
     ${GroupBy} = 'be', bu,
     ${GroupBy} = 'bu', bu,
     ${GroupBy} = 'account_alias', {account_name},
     ${GroupBy} = 'Account Name', {account_name},
     ${GroupBy} = 'account_id', accountid,
     ${GroupBy} = 'Account ID', accountid,
    NULL
)
CalculatedFields.Name: Group By
